\v 7 <a name="03801100700004" ll="SDBH:רעה:000001:Ingest" il="LB00014;BK00007;LB00001;BK00005;BK00004;BK00010;HK00009;LB00006;LB00013;NBGpb20140401b;Shepherd;Bolen00156;Bolen00369;AT Image00159;AT Image00247;AT Image00254;AT Image00556;Fauna0023">فَرَعَيْتُ</a> <a name="03801100700008" ll="SDBH:צֹאן:000000:Domestic Animals" il="LB00012;LB00017;LB00015;LB00014;NBGpb20140401b;NBGbs20120208-08;NBGbs20120710-139;tb111706002;Bolen00156;Bolen00369;AT Image00088;AT Image00159;AT Image00247;AT Image00556;Fauna0012">غَنَمَ</a> ٱلذَّبْحِ . لَكِنَّهُمْ أَذَلُّ <a name="03801100700020" tl="HOTTP4474">ٱلْغَنَمِ</a> . <a name="03801100700024">وَأَخَذْتُ</a> لِنَفْسِي <a name="03801100700030" ll="SDBH:מַקֵּל:000001:Tools">عَصَوَيْنِ</a>، فَسَمَّيْتُ <a name="03801100700034" ll="SDBH:אֶחָד:000003:Quantity|Frequency">ٱلْوَاحِدَةَ</a> «<a name="03801100700038" ll="SDBH:נֹעַם:000001:Willing">نِعْمَةَ</a>» وَسَمَّيْتُ <a name="03801100700044" ll="SDBH:אֶחָד:000003:Quantity|Frequency">ٱلْأُخْرَى</a> «حِبَالًا» <a name="03801100700052" ll="SDBH:רעה:000001:Ingest" il="LB00014;BK00007;LB00001;BK00005;BK00004;BK00010;HK00009;LB00006;LB00013;NBGpb20140401b;Shepherd;Bolen00156;Bolen00369;AT Image00159;AT Image00247;AT Image00254;AT Image00556;Fauna0023">وَرَعَيْتُ</a> <a name="03801100700058">ٱلْغَنَمَ</a>.
